title: Is This A Quote From Donald Trump Or Dialogue From Porn?
text:
Is This A Quote From Donald Trump Or Dialogue From Porn? It's closer than it should be. By Andy McDonald 
Comedians Lance Weiss and Brendan Fitzgibbons took to the streets and asked everyday people whether they could tell the difference between things Donald Trump has said and dialogue from pornographic motion pictures. (Sometimes called “porn” for short, I’m told by our industry-leading smut experts.) 
This is more difficult than it should be, given that he’s the president of the United States of America . Let’s see how they did! ALSO ON HUFFPOST These Photos Of The Trump Administration Say Pretty Much Everything These Photos Of The Trump Administration Say Pretty Much Everything 1
